channel.description:
Hey everyone!
I been working a while on a program that will, spam, and crash a server; and one that works on all types! And I have finally finished it! Now this program will log in multiple accounts (The longer you let it run, the more. I've hit 500 characters) and spam with whatever you choose it to spam.
A few pictures:
[img]http://img17.imageshack.us/img17/1433/ex1rnj.jpg[/img] [u][i][b](Ags4Life is my RL Username)[/b][/i][/u] [img]http://img32.imageshack.us/img32/4634/ex2m.jpg[/img]
Hope you like this! Now this program took days and days to make! And currently, I'm not giving it away for free. So, if you would like to download this program, there's a fee of USD$3.00. Please send the fee via, PayPal.
Send to: th3pl4c3@live.com
Once the small, and easy payment of $3.00 has been made, please send me an E-mail (th3pl4c3@live.com) stating that you have payed. Once I confirm it (takes less then 60 seconds), I will immediately send you the link to download this wonderful bot!
But act fast! This topic may be removed from the Forums quickly, so make your payments quick before this is gone and never seen again!
- Thank you for your interest. - Eric.
